sequenceDiagram
    participant Outlook as #160;#160;Outlook#160;#160;
    participant Item as #160;#160;Mail or appointment#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;in compose mode#160;#160;
    participant AddIn as #160;#160;Outlook add-in#160;#160;
    participant Exchange as #160;#160;Exchange#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;(on-prem, cloud)#160;#160;

    Outlook->>Item: #160;#160;User drafts new email or appointment#160;#160;
    Item->>AddIn: #160;#160;User opens add-in task pane#160;#160;
    AddIn->>AddIn: #160;#160;User interacts with the add-in task pane#160;#160;

    Note over AddIn: #160;#160;Manual task pane processing is interactive.#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;It can override automatic host/platform limits.#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;It supports manual signature selection.#160;#160;

    AddIn->>Exchange: #160;#160;Read mailbox, user, group, and signature data#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;(CLOUD_ENVIRONMENT, GRAPH_CLIENT_ID,#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;CustomCloudEnvironments)#160;#160;
    Exchange-->>AddIn: #160;#160;Data for signature selection#160;#160;
    AddIn->>AddIn: #160;#160;Apply powerful situation-aware custom logic#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;(CUSTOM_RULES_CODE)#160;#160;
    Note over AddIn: #160;#160;Can override signature, signature body,#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;and notification based on item context.#160;#160;
    AddIn->>Item: #160;#160;Insert selected or manually chosen signature#160;#160;
    AddIn->>Outlook: #160;#160;Show notification banner#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;(NOTIFICATION_TEXT)#160;#160;

    opt #160;#160;Logging#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;if DEBUG is true#160;#160;
        AddIn->>Item: #160;#160;Add logging output to body#160;#160;<br>#160;#160;(DEBUG)#160;#160;
